Alert-Handler version 0.0.1

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

	use warnings;
	use strict;
	use Carp;
	use Safe;
	use version;
	use warnings;
	use Crypt::GPG;
	use WWW::Curl::Easy;
	use XML::Bare;
	
On debian based systems install
	libcrypt-gpg-perl libwww-curl-perl libxml-bare-perl


